The Place of Many Paths

Wander and discover,
   a place where shadows
Whisper secrets,
And open doors to dreams.
The song builds layers of life,
Slips through the tree branches,
Twirls like dust in the night,
While the moon lifts our spirits.


- Gary Snyder
